print(Colorate.Horizontal(custom_gradient, "Gradient tÃ¹y chá»‰nh", 1))
```

### 4. Hiá»‡u á»¨ng Animation

```python
from colorful_style import Animate, Colors

# Typing effect
Animate.typing("VÄƒn báº£n Ä‘Æ°á»£c gÃµ tá»«ng kÃ½ tá»± má»™t cÃ¡ch mÆ°á»£t mÃ ...", Colors.rainbow, speed=0.03)
