# Pulse effect
Animate.pulse("VÄƒn báº£n nhá»‹p Ä‘áº­p", Colors.pink, duration=3)
Animate.pulse("Nhá»‹p Ä‘áº­p vá»›i mÃ u neon", Colors.neon, duration=2)

# Wave effect
Animate.wave("VÄƒn báº£n sÃ³ng", Colors.ocean, duration=3)
Animate.wave("SÃ³ng vá»›i mÃ u gradient", Colors.rainbow, duration=4)
```

### 5. Hiá»‡u á»¨ng Äáº·c Biá»‡t

```python
from colorful_style import Effects, Colors

